Construct a new KAM Path.

Parameters:
kam - the Kam the path was derived from
source - the source Kam.KamNode, must not be null
target - the target Kam.KamNode, may be null
edges - a list of edges; may be empty
Throws:
InvalidArgument - Thrown if any of kam, source, or edges is null, or if the resulting path does not make logical sense (e.g., kam is not the source node's KAM)
